  "time_ut": 1658289799,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc7\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Wigneswaran supports Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament CV Wigneswaran has announced that he has decided to give his vote to Deputy Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe."
      ],
